  "title": "Gallery Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>The candidate will be in charge of cleaning of the 4 main galleries spaces in Tanjong Pagar Distripark and 1 gallery space in Paragon.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>General cleaning, sanitizing, tidying and maintenance of the gallery areas,</li>\n  <li>Sweeping or scrubbing floors and surfaces.</li>\n  <li>Cleaning of the office and pantry areas.</li>\n  <li>Soft cleaning or dusting the sculptures or paintings on display or in store with appropriate tools</li>\n  <li>Sorting and removing trash, placing it in pickup areas, and cleaning garbage cans.</li>\n  <li>Following safety, sanitation, health and emergency procedures.</li>\n  <li>Occasionally, the gallery cleaner may be required to help to carry equipment or supplies between storage and work areas, or support in diverse gallery tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Physically fit</li>\n  <li>Good attention to details</li>\n  <li>Work 5 days per week: 3 full days and 2 half days at Tg Pagar Distripark and 2 half-days at Paragon weekly</li>\n  <li>Part timers also welcome.</li>\n</ul>",
