    "description": "<p>LINDA GALLERY PTE LTD</p>\n<p>Linda Gallery has been an active player in the arts industry ever since it was established in Jakarta, Indonesia in 1990.&nbsp; With the practice of more than two decades, Linda Gallery has made it its mission to provide art collectors, from all around the world, with premium quality Asian and Southeast Asian artworks. &nbsp;Linda Gallery serves as a communicative platform and commercial distributor for both art collectors and artists.&nbsp; It is in Linda Gallery's philosophy that it always deal with its customers and artists professionally, with utmost efficiency and sincerity.</p>",
